ls
```

* Confirmed `index.html` is present in `~/cluster`

```bash
scp ~/cluster/index.html banner@stapp03:/tmp/cluster/
```

* Entered `banner`'s password
* File `index.html` successfully copied to `/tmp/cluster/` on `stapp03`

